    • 字段详细资料

      • CLASS_AND_PROPERTY_CONVENTION

        public static final Convention CLASS_AND_PROPERTY_CONVENTION
        The default class and property conventions
        • Sets the discriminator key if not set to _t and the discriminator value if not set to the ClassModels simple type name.
        • Configures the PropertyModels. If the idProperty isn't set and there is a property named getId(), id or _id it will be marked as the idProperty.

      • ANNOTATION_CONVENTION

        public static final Convention ANNOTATION_CONVENTION
        The annotation convention.

        Applies all the conventions related to the default org.bson.codecs.pojo.annotations.

      • DEFAULT_CONVENTIONS

        public static final java.util.List<Convention> DEFAULT_CONVENTIONS
        The default conventions list

      • NO_CONVENTIONS

        public static final java.util.List<Convention> NO_CONVENTIONS
        An empty conventions list
